<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97527202210586></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97527202210586><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/quest.html?quest=271&mid=97527202210586 style='color: darkblue;'>Money Problems!!!</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Nov 26th 3:53 PM</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2> I have all the peices for the legs, wrsits, and boots... Only thing im missing is the dufrenites! I only have 90pp in the bank! thats not enough for ONE duf, much less 3! I am only level 21 and i cant seem to ever get a winning role when group camping things, for some odd reason i ALWAYS roll like a 3 or 1 or something really really low like that. =( Dunno what im gonna do, anyone know of any solo camps i could do to get money? I was thinkin TT's in Najena but when they double team me im in BIG trouble, any suggestions would be great! im on prexus server if you wanta help, im always  Nitsujlak (ogre shammy)Travullur(WE rouge) or my ogre warrrior Grumpz. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
