	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Fri, Jul 14th 5:20 PM</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[2.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>For those that haven't heard, the Lich is a 45th level Necro with a 35th level Skel pet. The lich is VERY powerful and has wiped out SEVERAL 50+ level parties. I would HIGHLY rec. that you bring either a Ranger (Good) or a Druid (better) who can track. Only reason that the  Druid is better (Even though skill in tracking will be less) is that he can Gate when you do, so you don't have to feel bad about leaving someone behind (I don't like doing that but it is better that ONE person die than two, harsh as that sounds).<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
